    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You did not enable it on the RA flak truck's sequences, but it definitely looks better with it so it should be added.\n\nAdditionally, it should be enabled on RA helicopters, they have 32 facings.\n\nFinally, `UseClassicFacingFudge: True` is not set on the rules defaults of vehicle + helicopter husks in either RA or TD, is that intentional? If not, that needs to be added as well.\n\nAs for regressions, the helicopter facing when landed on helipad is strange/wrong, but I haven't checked yet whether that's caused by this PR or on bleed already.\n"
  },
